<h3 id="åŒºé—´åŒ¹é…å…ƒç»„åŒ¹é…">åŒºé—´åŒ¹é…ã€å…ƒç»„åŒ¹é…</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>å¯ä»¥ä½¿ç”¨ä¸‹åˆ’çº¿ <strong>_</strong> å¿½ç•¥æŸä¸ªå€¼</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>å…³äº<strong>case</strong>åŒ¹é…é—®é¢˜ï¼Œå±äºæ¨¡å¼åŒ¹é…(Pattern Matching)çš„èŒƒç•´ï¼Œè¯·å¬ä¸‹å›åˆ†è§£</p>

    <pre><code class="language-objective-c">let count = 62
switch count {
case 0:
    print("none")
case 1..&lt;5:
    print("a few")
case 5..&lt;12:
    print("several")
case 12..&lt;100:
    print("dozens of")
case 100..&lt;1000:
    print("hundreds of")
default:
    print("many")
} // dozens of
  
  
let point = (1, 1)
switch point {
case (0, 0):
    print("the origin")
case (_, 0):
    print("on the x-axis")
case (0, _):
    print("on the y-axis")
case (-2...2, -2...2):
    print("inside the box")
default:
    print("outside of the box")
} // inside the box
</code></pre>
  </li>
</ul>

