<h3 id="å€¼ç»‘å®š">å€¼ç»‘å®š</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>å¿…è¦æ—¶letä¹Ÿå¯ä»¥æ”¹ä¸ºvar</p>

    <pre><code class="language-objective-c">let point = (2, 0)
switch point {
case (let x, 0):
    print("on the x-axis with an x value of \(x)")
case (0, let y):
    print("on the y-axis with a y value of \(y)")
case let (x, y):
    print("somewhere else at (\(x), \(y))")
      
} // on the x-axis with an x value of 2
</code></pre>
  </li>
</ul>

