<h3 id="æ ‡ç­¾è¯­å¥">æ ‡ç­¾è¯­å¥</h3>

<pre><code class="language-objective-c">outer: for i in 1...4 {
    for k in 1...4 {
        if k == 3 {
            continue outer
        }
        if i == 3 {
            break outer
        }
        print("i == \(i), k == \(k)")
    }
}
</code></pre>

